  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/32f52fbc9414a8f0562581a3410dc7dc.avif?t=1726817834\" width=610 height=150 /></span>.<br><br>Road to Devadatta is a first-person adventure game focused on story and puzzle solving in order to advance.<br>Explore ancient ruins as you unravel the mystery surrounding Devadatta!<br>Use your wits to escape from them, solve their ingenious (and sometimes deadly) puzzles and avoid being killed by the creatures that inhabit them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.poster.avif?t=1726817834\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.webm?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.mp4?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each trial will present you with a new challenge, where patience or speed may determine the outcome.<br><br>You'll encounter a variety of complex puzzles and physics puzzles that you'll have to solve in order to progress through the story. <br><br><strong>You are not alone</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/Fire1.gif?t=1726817834\" /></span><br><br><br>Danger may be very near, you have to be on the lookout for that strange creature obsessed with hunting you down.<br>What is it, why does it want to kill you?<br><br><strong>You're not alone</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/cf053d884001019151836b026e34346b.avif?t=1726817834\" width=610 height=150 /></span><br><br><i>Follow in the footsteps of Devadatta</i>.<br><br>Alo is Robert's nephew, with whom he spent his entire childhood. He hasn't heard from him for a long time and decides to go looking for him.<br><br>Alo will begin to search for answers and unwittingly follow in Devadatta's footsteps to discover the terrible secret behind his uncle's disappearance.<br><br><strong>You are not <br>you are <br>alone</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/8d47ab832923c45934abef8ddf16dbb3.poster.avif?t=1726817834\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/8d47ab832923c45934abef8ddf16dbb3.webm?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/8d47ab832923c45934abef8ddf16dbb3.mp4?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/32f52fbc9414a8f0562581a3410dc7dc.avif?t=1726817834\" width=610 height=150 /></span>.<br><br>Road to Devadatta is a first-person adventure game focused on story and puzzle solving in order to advance.<br>Explore ancient ruins as you unravel the mystery surrounding Devadatta!<br>Use your wits to escape from them, solve their ingenious (and sometimes deadly) puzzles and avoid being killed by the creatures that inhabit them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.poster.avif?t=1726817834\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.webm?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.mp4?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each trial will present you with a new challenge, where patience or speed may determine the outcome.<br><br>You'll encounter a variety of complex puzzles and physics puzzles that you'll have to solve in order to progress through the story. <br><br><strong>You are not alone</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/Fire1.gif?t=1726817834\" /></span><br><br><br>Danger may be very near, you have to be on the lookout for that strange creature obsessed with hunting you down.<br>What is it, why does it want to kill you?<br><br><strong>You're not alone</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/cf053d884001019151836b026e34346b.avif?t=1726817834\" width=610 height=150 /></span><br><br><i>Follow in the footsteps of Devadatta</i>.<br><br>Alo is Robert's nephew, with whom he spent his entire childhood. He hasn't heard from him for a long time and decides to go looking for him.<br><br>Alo will begin to search for answers and unwittingly follow in Devadatta's footsteps to discover the terrible secret behind his uncle's disappearance.<br><br><strong>You are not <br>you are <br>alone</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/8d47ab832923c45934abef8ddf16dbb3.poster.avif?t=1726817834\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/8d47ab832923c45934abef8ddf16dbb3.webm?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/8d47ab832923c45934abef8ddf16dbb3.mp4?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
